"===  FUNCTION  ================================================================
"          NAME:  Vim_CodeComment     {{{1
"   DESCRIPTION:  Code -> Comment
"    PARAMETERS:  -
"       RETURNS:  
"===============================================================================
function! Vim_CodeComment() range
	" add '" ' at the beginning of the lines
	for line in range( a:firstline, a:lastline )
		exe line.'s/^/"/'
	endfor
endfunction    " ----------  end of function Vim_CodeComment  ----------
